<p><img src="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/f/c/8/event_515685000.jpeg" border="0" /><br /><br /><strong>Narrowing the skills gap, one chapter at a time.</strong><br /><br />Welcome to <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/events/295936986/">Front-End Development Bootcamp</a></strong>. Let's begin.</p>
<p>The first step is to gain access to <strong><a href="https://frontendmasters.com/bootcamp/">Bootcamp Learning Path</a></strong>—a FREE series of training modules offered by <strong>Frontend Masters</strong>.</p>
<p>The second step is to post a brief update to <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53966604">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> which will acknowledge your commitment to begin this training opportunity. Nineteen Boston PHP members have signed up. I'm looking for 19 posts in the <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53966604">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> discussion area.</p>
<p>This week marks <strong>Sprint #1</strong>. The target is to complete <strong>Introduction to HTML</strong>, the first of nine modules in this Bootcamp. This module should take less than two hours to complete. Once finished, post an update to <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53972219">Bootcamp: Introduction to HTML</a></strong>.</p>
<p>For a complete list of all Modules and Sprint dates, access <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53971585">Master Discussion List—Front-End Development Bootcamp</a></strong>. Feel free to post whatever questions you might have in the <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53966604">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> discussion area.</p>
<p><strong>NOTE:</strong> I have adjusted the event on Meetup to continue registration through the end of September. Feel free to invite your tech-friendly friends and co-workers to join you on this Bootcamp journey. Rest assured, we have begun! <img src="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/s/img/981263258369601089/smileys/smile.gif" border="0" hspace="2" vspace="0" /></p>
